channel.title: Why is this happening
channel.description:
I am following the tutorials VERY carefully, doing EXACTLY as they tell me, when I save, Compile, and restart my server, nothing is edited, it's the same old Satan's Isle. I mean, I changed some Armor's stats, nicely edited some shops, moved a couple of things around.. But now I can't do anything. I tried making the XP higher when you train. Didn't happen. I tried making it say "Anon has logged in, BOW TO HIS FEET!" Didn't happen. You know what? FUCK IT. I'll just.. give my edited Satan's Isle to some random guy.. It really isn't that bad. I can't edit shit, so I am just wasting days of my life on this stupid server which I won't even end up running 3 hours before something fatal happens to the server and my week of editing is fucked. There HAS to be some way.. Unless it's my compiler.. Maybe it's not doing it's job? I'll try editing it, and adding Mod Taharok's perfect compiler..
Get back to me.
